    title: "Client Success",
    body: "Congratulations to my clients Vy Nguyen and Charlotte Mellington who will both appear in Emerald Fennell's 'Wuthering Heights' set for release in February 2026. Charlotte plays 'Young Cathy' and Vy plays 'Young Nelly'. They will star alongside Margot Robbie as Cathy and Jacob Elordi as Heathcliff.",
    image: "/images/wuthering-heights.jpg",
  },
  {
    date: "15 May 2025",
    title: "Through It All Together",
    body: "I am thrilled to join the team as Dialect Coach on the world premiere of Through it All Together at The Leeds Playhouse. Directed by Gitika Buttoo. The play will run from 23rd June \u2013 19th July.",
