    title: "Threshold",
    body: "I am thrilled to join the creative company of 'Threshold' directed by Tian Glasgow at The Royal Exchange Theatre in Manchester as Vocal Support. As an alumnus of the Young Company at The Royal Exchange Theatre, this will be a special production for me.",
