  },
  {
    date: "30 July 2024",
    title: "Anais Jessica Berinde Wins at the Young Artist Academy Awards",
    body: "Congratulations to Anais, she is fresh from her return from Hollywood after representing young U.K talent at the prestigious awards. Anais is a graduate from my ten-week coaching programme, which she took twice for twenty weeks in total, really honing her American accent \u2013 she is going to be one to watch!",
